{"record_id":"xiaocai:procurement_standard:source_backed_requirement_fields","source_id":"domain_seed:xiaocai:procurement_standard:source_backed_requirement_fields","title":"采购需求字段应保留来源和用途说明","content":"采购需求梳理应把项目目标、采购对象、数量单位、预算、交付地点、供应商资格、质量要求、验收口径和合同/付款约束整理成结构化字段，并保留来源引用。公开采购数据标准强调项目、标的、供应商、合同和里程碑等对象的结构化表达；xiaocai 可将这些作为字段完整性和可追溯性的基础参考。","metadata":{"domain":"xiaocai","tenant_id":"procurement_china","record_type":"procurement_standard","review_status":"seeded","confidence":0.82,"tags":["需求梳理","字段完整性","来源追踪"],"source_refs":[{"source_id":"public:ocds:data-standard"},{"source_id":"public:ocds:release-schema"}]}}
{"record_id":"xiaocai:procurement_standard:category_and_supplier_traceability","source_id":"domain_seed:xiaocai:procurement_standard:category_and_supplier_traceability","title":"品类与供应商检索应可追溯到分类和来源层级","content":"采购对象应尽量映射到明确品类、服务范围或物资类别，供应商检索结果应说明命中的来源库、品类关系、能力依据和风险提示。CPV 可作为公开品类词表参考；采购中国实例还应区分采购中国供应商库、会员 SaaS 中台供应商会员、智能体 SaaS 平台备选供应商库三类来源。","metadata":{"domain":"xiaocai","tenant_id":"procurement_china","record_type":"procurement_standard","review_status":"seeded","confidence":0.8,"tags":["品类","供应商检索","来源库"],"source_refs":[{"source_id":"public:eu:cpv"},{"source_id":"internal:procurement-china:supplier-optimization-v3"}]}}
{"record_id":"xiaocai:procurement_standard:ict_supplier_risk_baseline","source_id":"domain_seed:xiaocai:procurement_standard:ict_supplier_risk_baseline","title":"ICT/系统类采购应显式表达供应链风险和安全要求","content":"涉及 IT 与通讯、系统集成、数据通讯设备、服务器、软件平台或外部服务时，需求梳理应补充供应商能力、交付与运维责任、信息安全、连续性、数据处理、风险等级和验收材料。NIST 供应链风险管理指南可作为风险字段和供应商审查问题的公开依据。","metadata":{"domain":"xiaocai","tenant_id":"procurement_china","record_type":"procurement_standard","review_status":"seeded","confidence":0.78,"tags":["ICT采购","供应链风险","供应商评估"],"source_refs":[{"source_id":"public:nist:sp-800-161-r1"}]}}
